DIGEST
SB 405 Original 2026 Regular Session Talbot
Proposed law requires any nursing home resident or potential resident in a home that
receives an overall quality rating of one-star from the Centers for Medicare and Medicaid
Services (CMS) to receive individual counseling from the office of aging and adult services.
